			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>Mark Phillips </strong></span>works as a freelance writer in Ischua, New York. His memoirs have appeared in<em> Notre Dame Magazine</em>, <em>North Dakota Quarterly</em>, and the <em>New York Times Magazine</em>.</p><a href="/contributors/mark-phillips" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
	</div>
</div>

